WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.130 align:middle line:84%
-In the New Age
culture of today,

00:00:02.130 --> 00:00:05.390 align:middle line:84%
a common idea is that your
thoughts create your reality.

00:00:05.390 --> 00:00:07.500 align:middle line:84%
The truth is far
more complicated.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:08.990 align:middle line:84%
It seems as if we
exist in a world

00:00:08.990 --> 00:00:10.220 align:middle line:84%
where a huge amount
of reality has

00:00:10.220 --> 00:00:12.130 align:middle line:90%
already been created for us.

00:00:12.130 --> 00:00:14.700 align:middle line:84%
We can't just imagine
or wish it away.

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:18.360 align:middle line:84%
We can see that a new world view
or a new paradigm is emerging.

00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:20.450 align:middle line:84%
This world view
integrates Western science

00:00:20.450 --> 00:00:22.240 align:middle line:84%
with the world's
mystical traditions.

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:23.840 align:middle line:84%
Neuroscience is
learning a great deal

00:00:23.840 --> 00:00:26.050 align:middle line:84%
about the brain/mind system,
about how our thoughts

00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:28.440 align:middle line:84%
and emotions arise
in the brain, even

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:31.340 align:middle line:84%
though the hard problem of
consciousness remains unsolved.

00:00:31.340 --> 00:00:34.470 align:middle line:84%
The New Age idea that our
thoughts change our reality

00:00:34.470 --> 00:00:37.060 align:middle line:84%
might actually be a
foreshadowing of a future state

00:00:37.060 --> 00:00:39.430 align:middle line:84%
of development where
we're able to integrate

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:41.670 align:middle line:84%
extrasensory perception
into our world view.

00:00:41.670 --> 00:00:44.250 align:middle line:84%
At that point, rather than
breaking the laws of science,

00:00:44.250 --> 00:00:46.170 align:middle line:84%
the scientific world
view will have expanded

00:00:46.170 --> 00:00:47.880 align:middle line:90%
to include this awareness.

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:50.220 align:middle line:84%
When we reach that
level, the new age will

00:00:50.220 --> 00:00:52.910 align:middle line:90%
no longer be a fringe culture.

00:00:52.910 --> 00:00:55.980 align:middle line:84%
Instead, it'll be the reality
in which everybody now lives.

